race.comment: ALMOST (6) has missed the frame at his last couple but did finish in the minors in quick time three back (18.18) at this track in a NG. Better than latest and can atone here. GRID GIRL (4) goes very well this course and distance starting 21 times for nine wins and nine minors. Missed the frame latest (18.74) when fourth over 320m at this track in a NG. Can hit the frame with the right run. RED ROCK RATTLER (3) has missed the frame at his last two runs but could not have been more impressive the run prior in his superb 18.11 win at this track over 320m. Expecting another bold showing. MR. SNOW (1) placed last time and cannot be ignored. Something for the Multiples: MR. SNOW (1)
